					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1681463#post-2492852</guid>
				<title>In which I reference half a dozen tales, articles, and GoIs...</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1681463/ties-that-bind#post-2492852</link>
