				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Considering how much I have written about Anderson Robotics, you’d think I’d have a tale focused on the actual group of interest by now, and not just the SCP Foundation MTF that’s chasing after them. Well, here it is.</p> <p>I guess you could consider this to be an origin story of sorts, in addition to being the next stepping stone in this series of tales.</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" >TwistedGears</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" >TyGently</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=778357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="ProcyonLotor" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=778357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/procyonlotor" >ProcyonLotor</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" >minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1379080&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="Randomini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1379080)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/randomini" >Randomini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=304355&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="Silberescher" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=304355)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/silberescher" >Silberescher</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" >Agent MacLeod</a></span> for all the feedback they provided that allowed this to go from a rather rough draft to a polished product.</p> <p>Extra special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1460847896" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" >Kalinin</a></span> who provided the original inspiration for this tale waaaaaaaaaaaay back in December.</p> <p>Enjoy the tale.</p> <p><em>JC</em></p> 
